Integrate Dashboards Into Your Mobile Usersâ€™ Workflow

You can access and interact with dashboards in the Salesforce mobile app using various methods.

Use dashboards as you interact with Salesforce records by embedding them directly on a record layout, or making them available from a record page tab. To create a link from a record to a dashboard, use actions, buttons, and links.

Add your dashboard to a Lightning page for seamless access outside the Salesforce record context.

Make a dashboard available as its own navigation item on mobile by using web tabs.
